{"tid":2463650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布吉島成為泰國最早解封景點   已接種疫苗者免隔離","createTime":"2021-03-27T01:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T03:50:35.000Z","uid":391580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b875720e6f6f268efd298e7e3255ca666b84ea23","tid":2463650,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">日本台灣跟隊就可以準備搶疫苗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國旅遊部長披帕（Phiphat Ratchakitprakarn）稱由首相巴育（Prayut Chan-o-cha）領導的經濟小組，3月26日批准布吉島私營公司和商業團體的建議，讓島上至少70%的居民接種疫苗，為重新讓遊客登島觀光做準備。<br />\n<br />\n政府擬在嘗試重開布吉島後，再將計劃擴大到蘇梅島（Koh Samui）等其他觀光點，協助提振國家旅遊業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSjD1Knr1Pcnn8XskTNpPYXnp8XAU2M9jpsizfA9fMbhM?filename=uzCAtuK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuzCAtuK.jpg&h=da83adbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這項決定意味着，普吉島將比泰國其它地區提早開放3個月。其他地區預計10月才會對已接種的遊客重開。<br />\n<br />\n根據擬議計劃，島上至少466,587名民眾須接種2劑疫苗，部門將以確保有933,174劑為目標。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社26日引述普吉島旅遊協會主席普密吉滴（Bhummikitti Ruktaengam）本周較早時說，提前重開布吉島可增加逾300億泰銖的經濟收益，但是否成功重開，取決於國際疫苗護照協議，以及泰國與其他國家的談判，以允許遊客自由旅行。"},{"pid":"2920a04734efd952b4a94e3028148ffbc20b7044","tid":2463650,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"<em>但是否成功重開，取決於國際疫苗護照協議</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9144c97f0eebe7e1a2674c15ea095f5b3460ce","tid":2463650,"uid":182624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"你打科興人哋認唔認何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f195171120600e995b917dd1a555ba8b4b32444","tid":2463650,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"到時剩係得科興打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f3f8b3d4b2e3345a5f9198ed68f811bfdeec73","tid":2463650,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"布吉新樓盤（渡假屋）全部半價50%off"},{"pid":"4daa79969d8f95f93a15438762c864e11ea743cc","tid":2463650,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"到時又要搶科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4425d9887d1c04821ada72f703c6d190e10a2a6","tid":2463650,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"佢地係唔係唔比bno入境"}]}